EECS373 Project
Follow Me


MOTOR CONTROLLER
================

PWDATA BIT MAPPING:
--------------------------------
Bits		Purpose
--------------------------------
0 	 	RIGHT FWD/~REV
1 		LEFT FWD/~REV
2-8	 	RIGHT DUTY CYCLE
9-15	 	LEFT DUTY CYCLE
--------------------------------


WIRE CONNECTIONS:
-------------------------------------------
DEVICE		PIN	DEVICE		PIN
-------------------------------------------
SF-Expansion	F0	H-Bridge	IN2
SF-Expansion	F1	H-Bridge	IN1
SF-Expansion	F2	H-Bridge	IN3
SF-Expansion	F3	H-Bridge	IN4
-------------------------------------------


H-BRIDGE INFO:
-------------------------------
PWM Frequency		= 100Hz
Minimum Duty Cycle	= 40%
Maximum Duty Cycle	= 90%
VS (same as motors) 	= 7.3V
VLS 			= 5V
CSA 			= 0V
CSB 			= 0V
-------------------------------